{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-20116/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-20116"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["2:01:16"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, tracking"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man looks at a woman seated across from him."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20116/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-20116","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20116/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-20116"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20116/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20116/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20116/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20116/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20116/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20116/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20116/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20116/canvas/1/09ac39c5-151d-4d00-9d41-dbd16b288f45","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T15:01:48.999Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>It’s never made explicit whether Alma is confessing the details of her relationship with Reynolds to Dr. Hardy. At this moment, she may simply be describing her (intense) feelings of attachment, but the concerned look on the doctor’s face suggests that the entire film may indeed be what she has told Dr. Hardy during their fireside conversation. Sophie Durbin even suggests that the film’s contents may be filtered not only through Alma’s perspective and retelling but also that of Dr. Hardy, who provides a “medicalized interpretation of her stories” (Durbin, “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW47583754 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.perisphere.org/2025/03/14/psychoanalyze-me-mommy-making-sense-of-the-mother-role-in-phantom-thread/\"><u>Psychoanalyze Me, Mommy</u></a>”).&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20116/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:574.700956937799,100.64443779904303,291.107206937799,401.22532894736844"}}}]}]}]}